OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FITV News understands that Birmingham
OL,7,FCouncil is poised to pay out hundreds
OL,8,Fof millions of pounds to women workers
OL,9,Fincluding teaching assistants and
OL,10,Fcleaners, ITV News' Deputy Political
OL,11,FEditor Anushka Asthana reports
OL,13,FBirmingham Council is poised to pay
OL,14,Fout hundreds of millions of pounds to
OL,15,Fwomen workers including teaching
OL,16,Fassistants, carers, caterers and
OL,17,Fcleaners in order to finally settle
OL,18,Fthe thousands of equal pay claims that
OL,19,Fhave pushed the local authority to the
OL,20,Fbrink of bankruptcy.
