OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FITV News understands that councillors
OL,7,Fhave been invited to an "extraordinary
OL,8,Fmeeting" next Tuesday to discuss the
OL,9,Fsettlement.
OL,11,FTonight neither the council nor the
OL,12,FGMB union would confirm any details or
OL,13,Fspecify a figure but sources have told
OL,14,Fme that there could be a compensation
OL,15,Fpayment of around #250m, with an
OL,16,Fadditional lump sum that could result
OL,17,Fin up to #400m in total.
