OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FSources tell me the deal was struck
OL,7,Fbetween Birmingham Council's
OL,8,Fleadership - and the trade unions -
OL,9,Fwhich will see them pull back from
OL,10,Flegal action in around 6,000 cases.
OL,11,FIndividual workers could each gets
OL,12,Ftens of thousands of pounds in
OL,13,Fcompensation, but some could get much
OL,14,Fmore.
OL,16,FThe largest group to benefit are
OL,17,Flikely to be teaching assistants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
