OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FCritically, that higher figure was
OL,7,Fused as one of the key justifications
OL,8,Ffor triggering a section 114 notice -
OL,9,Fwhich is seen as a council effectively
OL,10,Fdeclaring bankruptcy.
OL,12,FMoreover, the notice was issued by the
OL,13,Fcouncil's finance director while the
OL,14,Fleader of local authority John Cotton
OL,15,Fwas on holiday.
