OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FThe actual size of the final liability
OL,7,Fwill raise serious questions over
OL,8,Fwhether the section 114 was necessary,
OL,9,Fparticularly given the dire
OL,10,Fconsequences for the city's residents,
OL,11,Fwho will see council tax rise by 21%
OL,12,Fover two years. Some insiders tell me
OL,13,Fthe council was suffering a lot of
OL,14,Fother problems, and was on a path
OL,15,Ftowards the 114 anyway, but they admit
OL,16,Fthat the sudden timing of the
OL,17,Fannouncement raised eyebrows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
