OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FOne source said the inflated figure of
OL,7,F#700m seemed to assume pay claims by
OL,8,Fall employees, which was never a
OL,9,Fpossibility.
OL,11,FBirmingham is one of a number of
OL,12,Fcouncils that have faced major equal
OL,13,Fpay claims, many revealed by ITV News.
OL,14,FThe basis of them tends to be that
OL,15,Fpredominantly female roles like those
OL,16,Fin the care sector, school kitchens,
OL,17,Fteaching assistants and cleaners, have
OL,18,Fless generous terms and conditions
OL,19,Fthan predominantly male roles like bin
OL,20,Fmen, road workers and in fleet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
