OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FThe equal pay scandal started to blow
OL,7,Fup for Birmingham when the council
OL,8,Fbegan issuing memorandum of
OL,9,Funderstanding documents (MOU's) to
OL,10,Ffemale workers in which they offered a
OL,11,Fpay settlement, but said that in
OL,12,Freturn the staff must sign up to an
OL,13,Fagreement settling "all equal pay
OL,14,Fclaims and related claims associated
OL,15,Fwith the subject matter".
OL,17,FBut when the GMB union saw the
OL,18,Fdocument they warned members not to
OL,19,Fsign, arguing they could be paid much
OL,20,Fmore through equal pay claims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
