OL,3,CBirmingham Council to settle equal pay
OL,4,Cclaim after bankruptcy, sources say
OL,6,FThe second issue was that the men had
OL,7,Fseen their jobs inflated from grade 2
OL,8,Fto 3 - but because of additions to
OL,9,Ftheir job description that did not
OL,10,Fline up with their actual tasks. As a
OL,11,Fresult the council is likely to
OL,12,Fabolish that role. That raises the
OL,13,Fother uncomfortable side to this
OL,14,Fdebate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
